{
  "stem": "6526.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe they used to come to Warsaw, they used to come-- But a lot of them came to Warsaw because maybe they had relatives in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe they were wealthy and they could set-- settle themselves in Warsaw because they had money.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was in the 19-- I think it was '35 or '36, I don't remember exactly the year, when there was a World Exhibition in France.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father had a sister in France.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the one who took the-- the chance to go to visit her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were special fares and so on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he came there and he saw the life altogether different, from a small town, Kalushin, of 10,000 population, to a city like Paris.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's like day in the summer with night in the winter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "To-- and he liked it very much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he said we're going to do-- do-- transfer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And by transferring, how do we do that?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there was a lot of relatives from Kalushin had in France.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the French relatives used to send money to their relatives in Kalushin, to the poor relatives.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So instead of them sending the money, he used to give the money to my aunt, to my father's sister.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she wrote us a letter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we paid out to the relatives.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is how we accumulated money in France to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then my father came back and he saw what happens here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We have a business, like a growing business like living with all the wealth and all this, this, this.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he start to think again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We're going to do, there's a new language.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And again, and with a business man who doesn't-- it doesn't have a trade.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My father's brother-in-law was my aunt's brother, was a tailor.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
